Title: Unpredictable Travel
DateModified: '2019-02-22'
DatePublished: '2019-02-22'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/unpredictable-travel
SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Novena Wijaya
AuthorCountry: Indonesia
Text: I've already visited 40 Countries around the world, and I have so many pictures
  in my laptop, but I want to share my experience everything I do in every countries.
  There's have so many conditions that I want to happy, sad, nervous, confused where
  I must to go to reach a destination. Sometimes I've heard from another people who
  thinks that traveling is so funny. Yeah it's true, but behind that, there so many
  uncontrollable and unpredictable situation that  We're never imagine about that
  situation. I want to share about my journeys everything I did. I want to start become
  a Travel Writer.
